QuestData.Title: Cenarion Concerns
QuestData.Description: Ey mon!$B$BDe Cenarion Circle sent Zen'kiki out here ta check out dem primals. I woulda been here sooner, but I had a little bit o' trouble gettin' my flight form ta work, mon.$B$BDe plants in dis place... I can hear dem talk. Dey be yellin' all the time. Angry an' violent yellin'.$B$BWould ya bring Zen'kiki back a leaf from dis Everbloom place dey be talkin' about? Maybe I can figure out what dey want.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect a Strangely-Glowing Frond from Everbloom.
